Proverbs 19-13 <t><f>ⓦ</f> A foolish son is ruin to his father, </t><t>and <f>ⓧ</f>a wife's quarreling is <f>ⓨ</f>a continual dripping of rain.</t>
Proverbs 19-14 <t><f>ⓩ</f> House and wealth are inherited from fathers, </t><t>but a prudent wife is <f>ⓐ</f>from the LORD.</t>
