Proverbs 19-22 <t>What is desired in a man is steadfast love, </t><t>and a poor man is better than a liar.</t>
Proverbs 19-23 <t>The fear of the LORD <f>ⓞ</f>leads to life, </t><t>and whoever has it rests <f>ⓟ</f>satisfied; </t><t>he will <f>ⓠ</f>not be visited by harm.</t>
